name: Blackbird - Cuco - Robusto
additionalNotes: The Blackbird Cuco is a medium-strength cigar that is hand crafted in the Dominican Republic. The Cuco’s Brazilian Colorado wrapper is draped over an Indonesian binder and fillers from the Dominican Republic. The Blackbird Cuco’s chocolatey and peppery flavors provide a well-balanced smoking experience that is definitely box worthy.
